data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!! Get your offer accepted now and move in before Christmas!!! Start the NEW year in your NEW home!  Check out this adorable cape cod with a concrete stamped exterior. All new windows and doors! Yard full of surprises...peach tree, strawberry patch, vineyard, perennials, herb garden, etc....plus a recessed heated pool and a funtime tiki bar. All items to keep the party going are there and will stay. Main floor master bedroom and main floor laundry is a definite plus. Newly tiled bathroom and hardwood floors throughout. Security system is on site and the services can be renewed by new owner if they so choose. 2.5 Car garage has a wood burning stove, as well as a gas heater and several work areas. All of this inside a fenced in yard!
